dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents Business Improvement Districts (BID) for the City of Milwaukee, WI in 2009. The dataset was originally published by the Department of City Development and the City of Milwaukee Information and Technology Division - GIS Section in 2009.[City of Milwaukee business improvement district (BID) polygons]
